  <data key="d1">"Merck is a pharmaceutical company that discovered lovastatin and conducted clinical trials for cholesterol drugs."&lt;SEP&gt;"Merck is the pharmaceutical company to which Vagelos belongs and is mentioned in the context of the drug treatment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Merck provided a small amount of lovastatin for the study conducted by Brown and Goldstein."</data>
