  <data key="d1">"Vagelos is a scientist at Merck who recognized the potential of cholesterol drugs and halted clinical trials based on safety concerns."&lt;SEP&gt;"Vagelos is the recipient of a letter from Brown and Goldstein regarding the drug treatment."</data>
