  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Compactin is a compound discovered by Endo that inhibits reductase and was initially tested in clinical trials."&lt;SEP&gt;"Compactin is a drug used in a study to observe its effects on reductase activity and cholesterol regulation."</data>
