  <data key="d1">"Lovastatin is a compound tested by Brown and Goldstein to increase LDL receptor levels and lower LDL cholesterol."&lt;SEP&gt;"Lovastatin is a similar compound to compactin, discovered by Merck, that also inhibits reductase."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c91b1e6b95b3dbfd48c0f0dd4b203819&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3b6a46d905558d3afdeb44a548f511f</data>
