<node id="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the Company, also not employing or engaging any investment banker, broker, or finder for the specified transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the same corporate umbrella as the Company, also subject to the same restrictions during the Effective Period."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are companies controlled by the parent company.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are companies that are owned or controlled by another company, often referred to as the parent company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are mentioned as entities that own or purport to own intellectual property along with the main company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are part of the Company and are also subject to financial disclosures and restructuring processes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are part of the Company and are also subject to the same laws and regulations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are part of the Company and operate in compliance with applicable laws and orders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are part of the Debtors, operating the business in compliance with specific laws and regulations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations under the Company, which are also subject to the same conditions and agreements as the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations under the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations under the main Company.")</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-91037fa6dbc130d80d50344ab6275e93&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f586118e4cd3d9e495c2d1ecb1dcfe1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f209b073ddfae25ccbc5d6c4b1b3bdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00138dfd30cd894bd371f1901cf69815&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa7e3853e32e9f1fed01da5b53618aca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9d3b8970106c262af65b92fb2a8f3b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00e68f4b96e22de0e8bc65f047078a94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d94ff967c8ad0500de2d6aa32d90efa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2593429f6940c350a32ac9825a7bf86a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e29100b495477a56239bf00a8c3b9ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d5b7f8816ad85d7f314b730dc9b6094&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1ad75b34be8f4c2caafc2636cd25519</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 1}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 25}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 93}]</data>
</node>
