  <data key="d1">"Transactions are the business dealings of the Company and its Subsidiaries, and no Causes of Action are pending or threatened, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transactions refer to specific business activities or agreements that are part of the restructuring process."</data>
