<node id="&quot;CHAPTER 11 CASES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Chapter 11 Cases are bankruptcy proceedings involving the Company and its Subsidiaries, which are exceptions to the absence of pending or threatened causes of action."&lt;SEP&gt;"Chapter 11 Cases refer to bankruptcy proceedings initiated by the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Chapter 11 Cases refer to bankruptcy proceedings initiated by the company.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Chapter 11 Cases refer to bankruptcy proceedings, which are mentioned as an exception in the context of pending or threatened causes of action."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0d5b7f8816ad85d7f314b730dc9b6094&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e29100b495477a56239bf00a8c3b9ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa7e3853e32e9f1fed01da5b53618aca</data>
