<node id="&quot;DEFINITIVE DOCUMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Definitive Documents are legal agreements related to the restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are part of the agreement or contract related to the company's operations.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents include legal agreements and plans related to the restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Definitive Documents are documents part of the Agreement and related transactions, and no Causes of Action are pending or threatened against the Company or its Subsidiaries, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."</data>
