<node id="&quot;ELTON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Elton is a biologist known for his work on ecosystem theory, comparing ecosystems to societies of organisms."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a researcher who noted the abundance of animals at the base of a food chain and the scarcity of apex predators like tigers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a scientist who proposed a model for the regulation of animal numbers, emphasizing the roles of predators, pathogens, parasites, and food supply."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a scientist who read Collett's book and wrote about lemming behavior in Animal Ecology."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a scientist who studied the pyramid of numbers and provided examples of animal populations in different ecosystems."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is described as explaining the regulation of animal numbers in nature and applied fields."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is mentioned in the context of serendipitous events in a scientist's journey, specifically with his lemming book in a Tromsø shop."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-44e345fb0c1f22aa3bf76aed2d40c63d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e12b39c6792276dd0ee66f4e9e6ceb7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e49097cc559bd14c5110941a42aea17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e37e299e058af586e801321f6b6d35dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5bc15638d83af338881cdee315b5d107&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f90dce699c970ebe061d69b3d6b78082&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94a8b002c80b038b73a7847ffd14aefa</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 17}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 78}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 123}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CANNON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cannon explains the regulation of ph"&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a physiologist known for his work on homeostasis, comparing the body to a collection of organs communicating through the nervous and endocrine systems."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a scientist who contributed to the discussion on the regulation of animal numbers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is another scientist whose concept of homeostasis is compared to Elton's model of regulating animal numbers, though Cannon did not use the term 'homeostasis' in this context."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is mentioned in the context of serendipitous events in a scientist's journey, specifically with his angry cats."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-44e345fb0c1f22aa3bf76aed2d40c63d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e12b39c6792276dd0ee66f4e9e6ceb7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94a8b002c80b038b73a7847ffd14aefa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e49097cc559bd14c5110941a42aea17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f90dce699c970ebe061d69b3d6b78082</data>
