</node>
<node id="&quot;CLASSICAL _VOIX MIXTE_&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Classical _voix mixte_ is a vocal technique that balances chest and head registers, used more in classical singing than in music theater."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e4e181dd5099e0ad2640bc3700a9eb29</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BELTING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Belting is a vocal technique characterized by a powerful, resonant sound often used in musical theater and pop music, distinct from the lighter qualities of the head register."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e4e181dd5099e0ad2640bc3700a9eb29</data>
</node>
