  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Younger, less experienced singers are typically more prone to technical issues or phonotrauma such as nodules, edema, and contact ulcers."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e4e181dd5099e0ad2640bc3700a9eb29</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MORE MATURE SINGERS WITH PROFESSIONAL PERFORMING CAREERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"More mature singers with professional performing careers are more likely to experience acute injuries, overuse and misuse injuries, or injuries following an illness."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e4e181dd5099e0ad2640bc3700a9eb29</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TECHNIQUE&quot;">
