  <data key="d1">"Technique refers to the methods and practices used in singing, including the use of different vocal registers and techniques like belting."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e4e181dd5099e0ad2640bc3700a9eb29</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PHONOTRAUMA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Phonotrauma includes conditions like nodules, edema, and contact ulcers, which affect the vocal folds due to improper technique or excessive strain."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e4e181dd5099e0ad2640bc3700a9eb29</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ACUTE INJURIES&quot;">
