  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Jacques Monod is mentioned alongside François Jacob in a quote."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacques Monod is mentioned as the original data source, suggesting he is a scientist whose laboratory notebooks provided the basis for the text."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e12b39c6792276dd0ee66f4e9e6ceb7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0643cd32ffcc8ca5432a080d756a1be6</data>
