</node>
<node id="&quot;TROPHIC LEVELS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Trophic levels refer to the positions of organisms in a food chain, with primary producers at the base and apex predators at the top."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5bc15638d83af338881cdee315b5d107</data>
