</node>
<node id="&quot;FRAMES (TEN PER HIVE BODY)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EQUIPMENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Frames (ten per hive body) are full-depth, 9½-inch units with wedge-style top bars and two-piece or split bottom bars, used to hold the beeswax foundation."</data>
