<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;BUSINESS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">67.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Business is the operational activities of the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company conducts the Business in the ordinary course of business consistent with past practice and in accordance with Applicable Law."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is responsible for preserving the Business and maintaining its relationship with various stakeholders during the Effective Period."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Business operations and conduct of the Company do not involve any pending or threatened Causes of Action, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."&lt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company operates in Business, and no Causes of Action are pending or threatened, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."&lt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company operates within the framework of its Business, which is subject to various laws and regulations."</data>
