  <data key="d4">74.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company and its Subsidiaries are part of the same corporate structure and are subject to the same restrictions during the Effective Period."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company and its Subsidiaries are related in that Subsidiaries are part of the Company's organizational structure."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are part of the Company's organizational structure."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subject to the same conditions and agreements as the Company, including Orders and Settlement Agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and its Subsidiaries are both subject to the same laws and regulations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and its Subsidiaries have not employed or engaged any investment banker, broker, or finder for the specified transactions."&lt;</data>
