  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Jefferies LLC has not been employed or engaged by the Subsidiaries for any of the specified transactions."&lt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Subsidiaries have not employed or engaged Jefferies LLC for any of the specified transactions."&lt;</data>
