  <data key="d4">21.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Subsidiaries engage in Transactions, and no Causes of Action are pending or threatened, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."&lt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Transactions are part of the Agreement and related documents, and no Causes of Action are pending or threatened against the Subsidiaries."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-aa7e3853e32e9f1fed01da5b53618aca</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;BUSINESS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">37.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are part of the Business and are subject to the same restrictions during the Effective Period."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are part of the Business and contribute to its operations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Business operations and conduct of the Subsidiaries do not involve any pending or threatened Causes of Action, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."&lt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Subsidiaries operate in Business, and no Causes of Action are pending or threatened, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2593429f6940c350a32ac9825a7bf86a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9d3b8970106c262af65b92fb2a8f3b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa7e3853e32e9f1fed01da5b53618aca</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;FORMER OR CURRENT PRODUCTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Any defects or quality issues related to Former or Current Products do not give rise to any Causes of Action against the Subsidiaries, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."&lt;</data>
