  <data key="d4">15.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries must follow the terms and conditions outlined in the Restructuring Term Sheet during the Effective Period."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Restructuring Term Sheet and related documents do not involve any pending or threatened Causes of Action against the Subsidiaries, except for those related to the Chapter 11 Cases."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2593429f6940c350a32ac9825a7bf86a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa7e3853e32e9f1fed01da5b53618aca</data>
