<edge source="&quot;PERSON&quot;" target="&quot;SUBSIDIARY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">49.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Person can engage in business transactions with a Subsidiary, including issuing, selling, or transferring shares."&lt;SEP&gt;"A Subsidiary can also engage in similar business activities as the Company, including issuing, selling, or transferring shares."&lt;SEP&gt;"A Subsidiary can engage in business transactions with another Person, including issuing, selling, or transferring shares."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Subsidiary also has employees and officers whose compensation and benefits may be changed."&lt;SEP&gt;"Two Persons can engage in business transactions with each other, including issuing, selling, or transferring shares."&lt;SEP&gt;"Two Subsidiaries can engage in business transactions with each other, including issuing, selling, or transferring shares."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4579467160834640f876588d93c8e141&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84496fb708a25e971b88a44322481b48</data>
