  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company Intellectual Property includes all registered intellectual property except those specified on Section 5.11(a)(ii) of the Company Disclosure Letter."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a1ad75b34be8f4c2caafc2636cd25519</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY REGISTERED INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 5.11(A)(II)&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Section 5.11(a)(ii) of the Company Disclosure Letter excludes certain intellectual property from the definition of Company Registered Intellectual Property."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a1ad75b34be8f4c2caafc2636cd25519</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY&quot;" target="&quot;COMPANY IT ASSETS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">5.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company IT Assets are not explicitly linked to Company Intellectual Property in the provided text, but both are organizational assets."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a1ad75b34be8f4c2caafc2636cd25519</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY&quot;" target="&quot;COMPANY SPECIFIED REPRESENTATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">4.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company Specified Representations do not directly relate to Company Intellectual Property, but both are part of the company's legal documentation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a1ad75b34be8f4c2caafc2636cd25519</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PERMITS&quot;" target="&quot;THE COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
