  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Singers rely on their vocal folds for sound production, which must be maintained for optimal performance."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6f1d4f8b586b63a9babc28a5d3da0cdb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SINGER&quot;" target="&quot;VOCAL ATHLETE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Singers are considered Vocal Athletes due to the physical and physiological demands placed on their bodies during performance."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6f1d4f8b586b63a9babc28a5d3da0cdb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SINGER&quot;" target="&quot;NUTRITION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">23.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Proper nutrition is essential for singers to maintain their vocal health and overall well-being during performances."&lt;SEP&gt;"Singers need to maintain proper nutrition to support their vocal health and overall well-being."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6f1d4f8b586b63a9babc28a5d3da0cdb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SINGER&quot;" target="&quot;PHYSICAL DEMANDS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
